data.title: Baker, Chet / Art Pepper "Picture of Health" [Blue Note Tone Poet Series]
data.meta_description: Limited 180gm vinyl LP pressing housed in deluxe gatefold jacket. Mono edition. Chet Baker & Art Pepper continued their fruitful collaboration with the 1956 Pacific Jazz album, Picture of Health (originally released as Playboys). The sextet for the session was loaded with top talent from the West Coast jazz scene including Phil Urso, Carl Perkins, Curtis Counce and Larance Marable. Blue Note Tone Poet Series features all-analog remastering.
